            "key": "smell",
            "icon": "👃",
            "sense": "SMELL",
            "text": "Petrichor — rain on hot pavement — which everyone recognizes: the scent of a universal memory — geosmin released by soil bacteria, triggering the same ancient recognition circuit in every human nose."
