        "subtitle": "Thinking of a Friend and They Call a Minute Later — Meaningful Coincidences Showing Everything Is Connected",
        "simple": "Have you ever thought of a friend and then they called you a minute later? That is called synchronicity. It is like the universe is giving you a little wink to show you that everything is connected. These moments feel like a pull because they make you stop and think about how big and mysterious life is. When these meaningful coincidences happen, they pull your attention to the fact that you are exactly where you are supposed to be.",
